Feature: Login 
  As a user, I want to be able to login to ikea website

  Background:
    Given that we are on ikea's website
    And that we accepted the standard cookie policy
    
  
  Scenario: Login Functionality
    Given user navigates to the website https://www.ikea.se/
    And there user logs in through Login Window by using Username as "USER" and Password as "PASSWORD"
    Then login must be successful.


  
  